item.title: 独家消息消息人士称，前 Pornhub 所有者对卢克石油公司资产感兴趣
item.description: 两位熟悉内情的消息人士称，奥地利商人贝恩德-伯格迈尔（Bernd Bergmair），包括 Pornhub 网站在内的一家成人娱乐集团的前多数股权所有人，已就购买受制裁的俄罗斯石油巨头卢克石油公司（Lukoil）的国际资产一事与美国财政部进行了接洽。【原文：Austrian businessman Bernd Bergmair, former majority owner of an adult entertainment group including website Pornhub, has approached the U.S. Treasury about buying international assets of sanctioned Russian oil major Lukoil , two sources familiar with the matter said.】

item.title: 玛格南冰淇淋预计 2028-29 年自由现金流可达 10 亿欧元
item.description: 联合利华下周将在阿姆斯特丹分拆冰淇淋业务上市，该公司周三表示，预计 2028-29 年将实现 8 亿至 10 亿欧元（9.332 亿至 11.7 亿美元）的自由现金流。【原文：Unilever's ice cream business, which is spinning off and listing in Amsterdam next week, expects to achieve free cash flow between 800 million and 1 billion euros ($933.2 million to $1.17 billion) in 2028-29, it said on Wednesday.】

item.title: ADP 称美国 11 月私营部门就业人数意外减少
item.description: 美国 ADP 就业报告周三显示，11 月份美国私营企业的就业人数意外下降。【原文：U.S. private payrolls unexpectedly declined in November, the ADP employment report showed on Wednesday.】

item.title: 尽管有禽流感贸易禁令，巴西 2025 年鸡肉出口仍将增长
item.description: 肉类游说团体巴西肉类协会（ABPA）周三表示，巴西鸡肉出口今年有望增长0.5%，达到532万吨，此前出口商避开了5月份禽流感疫情引发的贸易禁令，包括来自主要买家中国和欧盟的禁令。【原文：Brazilian chicken exports are expected to rise up to 0.5% this year to 5.32 million metric tons, meat lobby ABPA said on Wednesday, after exporters avoided trade bans triggered by a bird flu outbreak in May, including from key buyers China and the European Union.】

item.title: LSEG 将把金融数据整合到 ChatGPT 中，推动人工智能发展
item.description: 伦敦证券交易所集团（LSEG）周三表示，将把其金融数据和分析整合到 ChatGPT 中，并向其员工提供 OpenAI 的企业工具，进一步推动人工智能在整个金融市场的应用。【原文：LSEG will integrate its financial data and analytics into ChatGPT and make OpenAI's enterprise tool available to its employees, it said on Wednesday, deepening its push to embed artificial intelligence across financial markets.】

item.title: 美国证券交易委员会停止审查高杠杆 ETF 计划，理由是存在风险敞口
item.description: 美国证券市场监管机构暂停了对几家基金管理公司提出的新的高杠杆交易所交易基金提案的审查，并要求进一步澄清与这些产品相关的风险。【原文：The U.S. securities market regulator has paused the review of proposals for new highly leveraged exchange-traded funds from several fund managers and sought more clarity on the risks tied to the products.】

item.title: 梅西百货上调年度目标，对假日消费持谨慎态度
item.description: 梅西百货公司（Macy's）周三今年第二次上调了年度目标，并公布了令人惊喜的季度利润，因为这家百货公司长达数月的扭亏为盈努力开始出现回报。【原文：Macy's on Wednesday raised its annual targets for the second time this year and posted surprise quarterly profit, as the department store operator begins to see returns from its months-long turnaround efforts.】

item.title: 美元树因平价产品需求稳定而上调年度利润目标
item.description: 美元树公司（Dollar Tree）周三上调了年度利润预期，此前该公司的季度盈利超过预期，因为这家折扣零售商预计，对其价格实惠的必需品的稳定需求将有助于抵消关税引发的不确定性的影响。【原文：Dollar Tree raised its annual profit forecast on Wednesday after beating quarterly earnings estimates, as the discount retailer expects steady demand for its affordable essentials to help counter the impact of tariff-led uncertainty.】

item.title: 早间竞价：风险资产昙花一现，美联储给美元带来更多痛苦
item.description: 当今美国和全球市场的关键所在。【原文：What matters in U.S. and global markets today.】

item.title: 华尔街期货因降息希望而上涨，数据成为焦点
item.description: 由于投资者加大了对美联储本月降息的押注，并在等待新一波的经济数据，周三美国股指期货走高。【原文：U.S. stock index futures edged higher on Wednesday as investors ramped up bets on a rate cut from the Federal Reserve this month and awaited a fresh wave of economic data.】

item.title: 墨西哥国家石油公司（Pemex）的债务成为潜在合作伙伴的红旗，墨西哥正努力提高石油产量
item.description: 自墨西哥国家石油公司（Pemex）负责人呼吁合作伙伴帮助这家濒临破产的墨西哥国营石油公司开展必要的项目以提高日益减少的产量以来，已经过去了一个多月，但国内和国际公司尚未上钩。【原文：It has been over a month since the head of Pemex made a plea for partners to help Mexico's ailing state oil company on projects needed to boost dwindling production, but national and international companies have not yet bitten.】

item.title: 研究显示，人工智能公司的安全实践未达到全球标准
item.description: 根据未来生活研究所（Future of Life Institute）新版人工智能安全指数，Anthropic、OpenAI、xAI 和 Meta 等主要人工智能公司的安全实践 "远未达到新兴的全球标准"。【原文：The safety practices of major artificial intelligence companies, such as Anthropic, OpenAI, xAI and Meta, are "far short of emerging global standards," according to a new edition of Future of Life Institute's AI safety index.】

item.title: 美联储数据显示央行已停止亏损
item.description: 在 COVID-19 大流行之后，美联储似乎终于扭转了长达三年之久的前所未有的亏损局面，这与美联储执行货币政策的方式有关。【原文：The Federal Reserve appears to have finally turned the corner on a three-year-long string of unprecedented loss-making tied to how it has implemented monetary policy in the wake of the COVID-19 pandemic.】

item.title: 汉莎航空检查 11 架近期交付的空客飞机机身缺陷
item.description: 汉莎航空周三表示，将对最近交付的 11 架飞机进行检查，以发现制造商空中客车公司本周早些时候指出的可能存在的机身面板缺陷。【原文：Lufthansa on Wednesday said it will inspect 11 recently delivered aircraft for a possible fuselage panel flaw flagged by manufacturer Airbus earlier this week.】

item.title: American Eagle shares jump as celebrity campaigns to bolster holiday demand
item.description: American Eagle Outfitters' shares surged nearly 12% before the bell on Wednesday after the retailer lifted its annual sales forecast, betting on celebrity partnerships and marketing campaigns to boost demand during the holiday season.

item.title: 芯片制造商 Marvell 通过 Celestial 交易增强人工智能雄心，股价大涨
item.description: Marvell科技公司以32.5亿美元收购半导体初创公司Celestial AI，加深了投资者对这家芯片制造商进军下一代人工智能基础设施的信心，该公司股价周三盘前攀升9%。【原文：Marvell Technology shares climbed 9% premarket on Wednesday after its $3.25 billion deal to acquire semiconductor startup Celestial AI deepened investor confidence in the chipmaker's push into next-gen AI infrastructure.】

item.title: 全球会计机构就银行风险评估新模式进行咨询
item.description: 根据全球会计规则制定者提出的新模式，银行可以让投资者更清楚地了解它们是如何管理风险的，比如与利率变化相关的风险。【原文：Banks could give investors a clearer view on how they manage risks, such as those associated with changing interest rates, under a new model proposed by a global accounting rule-setter.】

item.title: 备忘录显示，央行批准维克拉姆-萨胡担任美国银行印度分行首席执行官
item.description: 路透社查阅的一份内部备忘录显示，印度央行已批准任命维克拉姆-萨胡（Vikram Sahu）为美国银行（Bank of America N.A.）印度首席执行官。【原文：India's central bank has approved the appointment of Vikram Sahu as chief executive officer of Bank of America N.A. in India, according to an internal memo reviewed by Reuters.】

item.title: 联合创始人称，WLF 将于 1 月推出真实世界资产产品
item.description: 世界自由金融公司（World Liberty Financial）联合创始人扎克-威特科夫（Zach Witkoff）周三在迪拜举行的一次活动上宣布，这家由美国总统唐纳德-特朗普家族支持的加密风险投资公司将于今年 1 月第一季度初推出一套真实世界资产产品。【原文：World Liberty Financial, a crypto venture backed by U.S. President Donald Trump's family, will launch its suite of real-world asset products at the beginning of the first quarter in January, co-founder Zach Witkoff announced on Wednesday during an event in Dubai.】

item.title: 中国可能在 2026 年追求 5%的 GDP 增长，以结束通货紧缩
item.description: 中国政府顾问和分析师表示，中国明年很可能会坚持目前5%左右的年度经济增长目标，这一目标要求政府在寻求摆脱通货紧缩困境的同时，保持财政和货币政策的开放。【原文：China is likely to stick to its current annual economic growth target of around 5% next year, government advisers and analysts said, a goal that would require authorities to keep fiscal and monetary spigots open as they seek to snap a deflationary spell.】

item.title: NHTSA表示，Rivian将因安全带问题召回近3.5万辆美国汽车
item.description: 美国国家公路交通安全管理局（NHTSA）周三表示，Rivian汽车公司计划召回34824辆美国汽车，原因是安全带预紧线受损，可能无法正确束缚驾驶员的安全带，增加碰撞受伤风险。【原文：Rivian Automotive plans to recall 34,824 U.S. vehicles due to a damaged seat belt pretension cable that may fail to properly restrain the driver's seat belt, increasing crash injury risk, the U.S. National Highway Traffic Safety Administration (NHTSA) said on Wednesday.】

item.title: 文件显示，中国力士乐计划在越南生产游戏机
item.description: 中国的苹果耳机制造商Luxshare-ICT公司在给当地政府的一份建议书中说，该公司计划从明年起在越南生产游戏机，年产能可达450万台。【原文：Chinese Luxshare-ICT, Apple's airpods maker, is planning to produce game consoles in Vietnam with annual capacity of up to 4.5 million units starting from next year, the company said in a proposal to local authorities.】

item.title: 沃尔沃汽车公司称美国市场低迷，11 月销量下降 10
item.description: 总部位于瑞典的沃尔沃汽车公司（Volvo Cars）周三报告称，由于贸易关税压力和美国需求低迷，该公司 11 月份销量下滑，延续了今年以来的颓势。【原文：Sweden-based Volvo Cars on Wednesday reported a slump in November sales, continuing a decline this year amid pressure from trade tariffs and subdued demand in the United States.】

item.title: 雨果-博斯（Hugo Boss）在战略调整中将目标定为长期 12% 的营业利润率
item.description: 德国时尚集团雨果博斯（Hugo Boss）周三表示，作为战略调整的一部分，该公司的目标是在中长期内实现约 12% 的营业利润率。【原文：German fashion group Hugo Boss on Wednesday said that it aims to achieve an operating profit margin of around 12% over the medium-to-long term as part of a strategic overhaul.】

item.title: 解说：陆地空间如何成为 SpaceX 最大的中国挑战者
item.description: 陆地空间公司已成为中国最先进的私营火箭公司，也是中国最接近埃隆-马斯克的 SpaceX 公司的公司，它追随美国竞争对手，将未来押注在可飞行多次的火箭上。【原文：LandSpace has become China's most advanced private rocket company and the country's closest equivalent to Elon Musk's SpaceX, following U.S. rivals in betting its future on rockets that can fly more than once.】

item.title: 可重复使用火箭：迄今为止谁取得了哪些成就？
item.description: 中国的朱雀三号可重复使用火箭由私营公司陆地空间开发，虽然周三未能成功着陆，但它的首次发射将全球可重复使用火箭的竞争推到了聚光灯下。【原文：China's Zhuque-3 reusable rocket, developed by private firm LandSpace, failed to make a successful landing on Wednesday, but its debut launch has thrust the global race for reusable rockets into the spotlight.】

item.title: 空中客车公司因机身缺陷下调 2025 年商用飞机交付目标
item.description: 空中客车公司周三将其2025年的商用飞机交付目标下调至约790架，原因是供应商的机身面板质量问题影响了其A320生产线。【原文：Airbus on Wednesday lowered its commercial aircraft delivery target to around 790 aircraft for 2025 due to a supplier quality issue on fuselage panels impacting its A320 line.】

item.title: Binance 任命 Yi He 为联席首席执行官
item.description: 加密货币交易所 Binance 周三表示，已任命联合创始人 Yi He 担任公司联席首席执行官。【原文：Cryptocurrency exchange Binance has appointed co-founder Yi He as its co-chief executive, the company said on Wednesday.】

item.title: 文件显示，富士康子公司计划扩大在越南的生产
item.description: 根据一份发给北宁省环保部门的公司文件，台湾电子制造商富士康的子公司富山科技正在申请在越南扩大生产的许可，以生产 Xbox 游戏机和其他电子零件。【原文：Fushan Technology, a subsidiary of Taiwanese electronics manufacturer Foxconn, is seeking a permit to expand production in Vietnam to make Xbox game consoles and other electronic parts, according to a company document sent to Bac Ninh province's environmental department.】

item.title: 早间竞价：风险上、风险下、风险上
item.description: Rae Wee 对欧洲和全球市场未来一天的展望【原文：A look at the day ahead in European and global markets from Rae Wee】
